Also: When I click on Git URL       I eventually get message Unable to display repository contents at this time. Refresh the browser to try again."  Refresh does not work.  FYI: Running Windows 10 Enterprise on Surface Pro 3   Also:  Works on my phone but not a great work environment. Thank you for your help!"
